storage rights. And I got to England just in time to 
start programming and building up facilities for

28:43.976 --> 28:57.215
those units that just two or three years ahead I had 
helped facilitate over there in France. Chaumont

28:57.235 --> 28:59.779
actually moved from The unit at Chaumont, where 
